syntax:<tag_name attribute="Value">...</tag_name>



example :

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Example of HTML Attributes</title>
</head>

<body>
   <a href="https://www.tutorialspoint.com">Visit our homepage</a>   <!-- here href is attribute and link is value -->
</body>

</html>
